QuestData.Title: Stalled Negotiations
QuestData.Description: The Warchief's whereabouts are unknown! But we have to keep his plan moving forward. $n, you look like you can get things done.$B$BOur negotiations with the Dragonmaw have stalled. Their Warchief is... not what we expected. I need you to go in there and get negotiations back on track.$B$BMeet with Ornak on the shore, he'll fill you in.$B$BTalk to Horzog on deck here for quick transportation to the shore.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Ornak in Dragonmaw Port. Horzog can provide you with quick transportation to the shore.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Ornak in Dragonmaw Port. Horzog can provide you with quick transportation to the shore.
QuestData.RewardText: I'm glad you're here, $c. Perhaps a seasoned veteran of the Horde's campaigns in Northrend and elsewhere can talk some sense into the Dragonmaw leadership...
